short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Show SJR rank informations from SciMagoJr on the citation generator

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
It actually show the Best Quartile, SJR, and Rank on SciMagoJr.

And it's working only on the scribbr citation generator.

Feel free to request any improvements on the github repository.

NB: It's using SciMagoJr Data from 2023
